nter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/159076/', '', 'Felodipine, Amlodipine, Bisoprolol, Hydrochlorothiazide, Indapamide', 'Vincristine, Cabazitaxel, Vinblastine, Topotecan, Teniposide, Vinorelbine, Etoposide', 1767369485);
